name: Handmade Phone Case for iPhone 5 in gray with pink heart
description:
This is a listing for one hand-crocheted Phone Case for Iphone 5 model. 
I try to specify the color as precise as possible. (other colors avalaible - see shop).

Made out of 100% organic cotton it will keep your phone without scratches and safe. The case is soft and could be washed (30°C machine wash. Do not bleach, do not tumble dry; dry clean with any solvent except trichloethylene).

The size of one Phone Case is to fit an Iphone 5. 
Please note: all cases are handmade, so minor alterations are possible.

Please read my shop policies before making the purchase.
